              <title xml:lang="en">I. A work entitled "the Book of the Vowel-points of the Holy Scriptures,"</title>
              <rubric xml:lang="syr">ܥܠ ܚ̇ܝܠ̣ܗ ܕܡܪܢ ܝܫܘܥ ܡܫܝܚܐ: ܡ̇ܫܪܝܢܢ ܕܢܟܬܘܒ: ܟܘܪܣܐ ܕܫܡ̈ܗܐ ܕܟܬܒ̈ܐ ܩܕܝ̈ܫܐ. ܩܕܡܝܬ ܫ̈ܡܗܐ ܕܟܬܒܐ ܕܒܪܝܬܐ ܘ܀ܘ</rubric>
              <note>similar in its general character to <bibl>Add. 12,138<ptr target="http://syriaca.org/manuscript/10"/>
