                <note>These tracts have been edited by <persName>the Abbé Martin</persName>, and in part by <persName>Dr. Phillips</persName>, in the works cited above. On <persName>Thomas the deacon</persName> see, in particular, <persName>Dr. Phillips’</persName> <bibl>third Appendix, p. 90.</bibl>
                </note>
              </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="b9" n="52">
                <locus from="242a">Fol. 242a</locus>
